author: Inside Edition
description: Over 60 million people died in 2025. Among them was Pope Francis, the first Latin American leader of the Catholic Church. In December, Hollywood legend Rob Reiner and his wife Michele were killed in their home. Several other Hollywood figures passed away this year, including director David Lynch and actors Diane Keaton and Robert Redford. Boxer George Foreman, heavy metal pioneer Ozzy Osbourne, and Beach Boy Brian Wilson also left us in 2025.
title: Remembering Those We Lost In 2025
